   "source": [
    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# Duplicate Text Detection\\n\",\"**NLP Project 20 of 100** — Find duplicate or near-duplicate documents using TF-IDF cosine similarity and MinHash.\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Learning Objectives\\n\",\"1. Detect exact and near-duplicate texts.\\n\",\"2. Implement cosine similarity and MinHash approaches.\\n\",\"3. Set appropriate similarity thresholds.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import numpy as np, pandas as pd, re, matplotlib.pyplot as plt, seaborn as sns\\nfrom sklearn.feature_extraction.text import TfidfVectorizer\\nfrom sklearn.metrics.pairwise import cosine_similarity\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\nsns.set_style('whitegrid')\\n%matplotlib inline\\nSEED = 42; np.random.seed(SEED)\\nprint('Loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"# Synthetic dataset with known duplicates\\noriginals = [\\n    'Machine learning is transforming how we analyze data in business.',\\n    'Python is the most popular programming language for data science.',\\n    'Climate change requires immediate global action from all nations.',\\n    'The stock market experienced significant volatility this quarter.',\\n    'Artificial intelligence will reshape the healthcare industry.'\\n] * 10\\n\\nnear_dupes = [t.replace('is','was').replace('the','a') + ' Additional noise.' for t in originals[:10]]\\n\\ntexts = originals + near_dupes + ['Completely unrelated text about cooking recipes.'] * 5\\nlabels = ['original']*50 + ['near_dupe']*10 + ['unique']*5\\ndf = pd.DataFrame({'text': texts, 'type': labels})\\ndf = df.sample(frac=1, random_state=SEED).reset_index(drop=True)\\nprint(f'Shape: {df.shape}, Types: {df[\\\"type\\\"].value_counts().to_dict()}')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## TF-IDF Cosine Similarity\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"tfidf = TfidfVectorizer(max_features=5000)\\nX = tfidf.fit_transform(df['text'])\\nsim_matrix = cosine_similarity(X)\\n\\n# Find duplicates above threshold\\nTHRESHOLD = 0.85\\npairs = []\\nfor i in range(len(df)):\\n    for j in range(i+1, len(df)):\\n        if sim_matrix[i,j] > THRESHOLD:\\n            pairs.append((i, j, round(sim_matrix[i,j], 3)))\\n\\nprint(f'Duplicate pairs found (sim > {THRESHOLD}): {len(pairs)}')\\nfor i, j, sim in pairs[:5]:\\n    print(f'  [{i}] vs [{j}]: sim={sim}')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"plt.figure(figsize=(8,6))\\nsns.heatmap(sim_matrix[:20,:20], cmap='YlOrRd', vmin=0, vmax=1)\\nplt.title('Similarity Matrix (first 20 docs)'); plt.tight_layout(); plt.show()\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **Cosine similarity on TF-IDF is effective** for finding near-duplicate documents.\\n\",\"- **Threshold of 0.85** balances precision and recall for deduplication.\\n\",\"- **For large corpora, use MinHash/LSH** for scalable approximate matching.\\n\",\"- **Deduplication is critical** for training data quality in ML.\"]}\n",
    " ],\n",
